abstract: German thin-film solar cell manufacturer Sulfurcell closed on a $133.7 million round, which was led by Intel Capital with a $37.7 million contribution.
lead_paragraph: German thin-film solar cell manufacturer Sulfurcell closed on a $133.7 million round, which was led by Intel Capital with a $37.7 million contribution.

headline.main: Intel Capital Invests $37.7 Million in Sulfurcell
